    "By incorporating these methods, our goal is to make the proposed network more robust and reliable.",
    "ConclusionIn conclusion, this work addresses the limitations of traditional convolutional networks in capturing complex semantic relationships from multi-scale ground objects in remote sensing scene images.",
    "To overcome these challenges, we introduced the Residual Channel-Attention (RCA) network, a novel and lightweight solution designed to enhance feature extraction and classification accuracy in remote sensing tasks.",
    "The RCA network's key innovations lie in its integration of residual connections and a channel-attention mechanism.",
    "The residual connections enable efficient multi-scale feature extraction, allowing the network to capture both fine and coarse details."
